dct_title_s: Belgii Novi, Angliae Novae, et partis Virginiae : novissima delineatio
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Dedicated to Gualthero de Raet. State 2 according to Campbell, between 1660-1663; Burden gives date as ca. 1660. Appears in: Jansson's Atlas contractus, sive Atlantis majoris compendium ..., 1666, with text on verso. Includes ill.
